        "title": "P2 — `agent.py`",
        "content": "\nHighest-value gaps: `cmd_db_new`'s date-window/group-truncation logic (subtle — truncates only at `first_seen` group boundaries) and `_normalize_ats`'s tag-aware regex (must not touch attributes or `<style>`/`<script>`).\n\n```python\n",
        "level": 2
